Class CustBookingHistoryPageController

  • java.lang.Object
    • screensframework.CustBookingHistoryPageController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable, ControlledScreen, CustToolbar

    public class CustBookingHistoryPageController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable, ControlledScreen, CustToolbar
    Controller class for the Booking History page. Allows customers to see their past bookings and delete any bookings that haven't taken place yet.
    Author:
    Mark Backhouse

      • bookingHistory

        java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.List<java.lang.String>> bookingHistory
        A Map of key:value pairs that will contain the Customer's Booking History. The keys are the Listing IDs and the values are Lists of Strings of the names of the seats the Customer has booked.
